CounselorAdapter ..> Counselor
AppointmentAdapter ..> Appointment
StudentAppointmentAdapter ..> Appointment
TimeSlotAdapter ..> TimeSlot
TimeSlotAdapter +-- OnBookClick

' ════════════════════════════════════════
