' ════════════════════════════════════════

StudentHomeActivity ..> UserRepository
StudentHomeActivity ..> AppointmentRepository
StudentHomeActivity ..> FeedbackRepository
StudentHomeActivity ..> CounselorRepository
StudentHomeActivity ..> EmergencyDialogFragment
StudentHomeActivity ..> QuizActivity
StudentHomeActivity ..> CalendarActivity
StudentHomeActivity ..> HistoryActivity
StudentHomeActivity ..> CounselorListActivity

BookingActivity ..> AvailabilityRepository
BookingActivity ..> AppointmentRepository
BookingActivity ..> AvailabilitySchedule
BookingActivity ..> TimeSlotAdapter
BookingActivity ..> BookingConfirmationFragment
BookingActivity ..|> OnBookClick

CalendarActivity ..> AppointmentRepository
HistoryActivity ..> AppointmentRepository
QuizActivity ..> CounselorListActivity
QuizActivity ..> CounselorRepository

' ════════════════════════════════════════
'  RELATIONSHIPS — Counselor UI → Repos
' ════════════════════════════════════════

CounselorDashboardActivity ..> AppointmentRepository
CounselorDashboardActivity ..> AvailabilityRepository
CounselorDashboardActivity ..> CounselorRepository
